{"type": "article", "id": 6867, "title": "The Carry Out 钱包", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-27T07:48:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143107871Pw4jVnuWR3BLt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">美国配件品牌 Bellroy 最近推出了一款名为「 The Carry Out 」的钱包，希望能够满足人们对于钱包空间的各种需求。设计团队将 The Carry Out 的内部空间进行了精细的划分，使其可以同时收纳 16 张卡、手机、护照、签字笔、纸币、硬币，甚至连 SIM 卡都有专门存放的地方，避免用户四处翻找这些微小物件。此外，The Carry Out 还配置了一个小的零钱夹，可以拆卸下来单独使用。提供黑、棕、蓝以及卡其色 4 种选择，定价 169.95 美元（约合人民币 1064 元），<a href=\"http://bellroy.com/wallets/carry-out-wallet#blue_steel\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143103qJ9AVrGH0eXO2LSp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143104jzG6qyKgO8kZh91w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143104csyOF6T9XrvtI5zx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143105nbkOoC5J0HmSQEcy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143106WP7u0n9T5tD2Lpsd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143106C4IeXtga51rW7Oho.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}